      <div class="msgContentFrame"><div class="msgQuote"><div class="source">Quote:</div><div class="orig">Use this forum for specific feedback and suggestions to the developer, not the players. This forum will be monitored by the game developers. To keep out general discussion and keep the true feedback from scrolling too quickly, it will be more heavily moderated than our other forums.</div></div> <br /> <br />This means: <br /> <br />* New threads are for providing feedback to SE.  Not for general discussion of the game itself. <br /> <br />* Posts in threads are to be kept strictly <u>on-topic</u>.  Post your feedback about the subject of the thread, and move on.  Debating opinions with other users not specifically related to the topic is for the <a href="HTTP://ffxiv.zam.com/forum.html?game=268" rel="external" title="ffxiv.zam.com/forum.html?game=268">General Discussion Forum</a>, and said posts will be removed. <br /> <br />* Trolling will absolutely not be allowed.  Again, take it to General Discussion. <br /> <br />* Please try to post feedback in a constructive, intelligent way. <br /><i>I HATE UR GAME SE!</i> -- Not constructive. <br /><i>I hate that X feature of the game exists/does not exist/is the way it currently is, and here's my idea(s) of what should be changed.</i> -- Constructive. <br /> <br /> <br />This is the place to get your voice heard by SE.  And yes, they are listening. <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct 13th 2010 12:38pm by Osarion  Lock Thread: </span></i> <br /> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct 27th 2010  4:42am by Osarion </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/400681.png" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
